kg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E9%2587%258B%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A-%25E7%25BE%2585%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2581%25B0-%25E6%258F%259B%25E5%258F%2596%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E6%259B%25B4%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E5%2580%25A1%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A1%25A1%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A8%2581%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%2593%25B4%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E6%259B%25B4%25E5%25B0%2591%25E9%2599%2590%25E5%2588%25B6%2F&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj3%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=abd2740a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E9%2587%258B%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A-%25E7%25BE%2585%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2581%25B0-%25E6%258F%259B%25E5%258F%2596%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E6%259B%25B4%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E5%2580%25A1%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A1%25A1%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A8%2581%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%2593%25B4%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E6%259B%25B4%25E5%25B0%2591%25E9%2599%2590%25E5%2588%25B6%2F&h=8115f213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%86%8D%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B%E9%9B%A2%E6%B8%AF%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A-%E7%BE%85%E5%86%A0%E8%81%B0-%E6%8F%9B%E5%8F%96%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%9B%B4%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%80%A1%E8%AD%B0%E5%88%B6%E8%A1%A1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A8%81%E6%AC%8A%E6%93%B4%E5%BC%B5%E6%9B%B4%E5%B0%91%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6/</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:27:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真係唔知醜<br />\n講什麼國際線<br />\n你能夠做什麼<br />\n你是否能夠做得好過袁彌明爸爸<br />\n若果什麼也不識<br />\n學人打什麼國際線<br />\n人哋出嚟一個月<br />\n好過你出嚟幾年<br />\n幫唔到手<br />\n環阻住地球轉<br />\n是否教育現在真是這麼失敗<br />\n完全沒有自知之明! <br />\n</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:45:50.000Z","msg":